com.github.dm.jrt.core.builder

Interface RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    IN - the input data type.
    OUT - the output data type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    InvocationConfigurable<RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>>, InvocationConfiguration.Configurable<RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>>, Routine<IN,OUT>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRoutineBuilder

    public interface RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>
extends InvocationConfigurable<RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>>, Routine<IN,OUT>
    Interface defining a builder of routine objects.

    Note that when the invocation is started directly from the builder, a new routine instance is implicitly created.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 11/11/2014.
